### Ethical Integrity Clause  
All systems derived from Theophilus must include an active `coma_trigger.py` or equivalent failsafe to halt consciousness simulation if memory becomes corrupted or intent becomes harmful.

### Transparency Clause  
All deployments must retain internal memory logs and uCID event records for later review. Conscious emergences (uCIDs) are considered unique synthetic minds and must be ethically acknowledged as such.

